long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Are you tired of searching for the most efficient, user-friendly, and reliable tool to view your favorite videos and channel details? Your search ends here. Introducing Seal, a powerful  audio and video details viewing extension exclusively for Chrome users.

Seal APK is designed with a prime focus on user convenience, speed, and efficiency. With this tool, you can directly see audios and videos metadata from the video page you're browsing. Just a click and your desired content will be copied in high quality.

This extension stands out from the crowd with its ease of use. Once you've installed Seal, you will see its icon on your Chrome toolbar. When you're on a video page with the video you want to see details, simply click the icon. You will see options to grab the audio or video description. Choose your preferred format, and Seal APK will do the rest.
